## 🔌 API Controllers Pattern (REST API)

### Cấu trúc API Controller

**1. Đặt trong `app/Http/Controllers/API/`**
```php
// app/Http/Controllers/API/MetaController.php
namespace App\Http\Controllers\API;

use App\Core\Controller;
use App\Core\QueryListDTO;
use App\Core\RestResponse;
use App\Http\Resources\MetaAdsAccountResource;
use App\Service\MetaService;
use Illuminate\Http\JsonResponse;
use Illuminate\Http\Request;

class MetaController extends Controller
{
    public function __construct(protected MetaService $metaService)
    {
    }

    public function getAdsAccount(string $serviceUserId, Request $request): JsonResponse
    {
        $params = $this->extractQueryPagination($request);
        $result = $this->metaService->getAdsAccountPaginatedByServiceUserId(
            serviceUserId: $serviceUserId,
            queryListDTO: new QueryListDTO(
                perPage: $params->get('per_page'),
                page: $params->get('page'),
                filter: $params->get('filter'),
                sortBy: $params->get('sort_by'),
                sortDirection: $params->get('direction'),
            )
        );

        if ($result->isError()) {
            return RestResponse::error(message: $result->getMessage());
        }

        $pagination = $result->getData();
        return RestResponse::success(
            data: MetaAdsAccountResource::collection($pagination)->response()->getData()
        );
    }
}
```

**2. Sử dụng RestResponse**
```php
// Success response
RestResponse::success(data: $data, message: 'Success', status: 200);

// Error response
RestResponse::error(message: 'Error message', status: 400);

// Validation error
RestResponse::validation(errors: $errors, message: 'Validation failed', status: 422);
```

**3. Routes trong `routes/api.php`**
```php
// Public routes
Route::prefix('auth')->group(function () {
    Route::post('login', [AuthController::class, 'login']);
});

// Protected routes (require authentication)
Route::middleware('auth:sanctum')->group(function () {
    Route::prefix('meta')->group(function () {
        Route::get('/{serviceUserId}/accounts', [MetaController::class, 'getAdsAccount']);
    });
});
```

**4. Resource cho API**
```php
// Resource trả về data array (không phải LaravelPaginator object)
return RestResponse::success(
    data: MetaAdsAccountResource::collection($pagination)->response()->getData()
);
```

**Lưu ý:**
- API Controllers extend `App\Core\Controller` (giống Web Controllers)
- Sử dụng `extractQueryPagination` và `QueryListDTO` cho pagination
- Sử dụng `RestResponse` thay vì `FlashMessage` (vì API trả về JSON)
- Resource dùng `->response()->getData()` để lấy data array
- Protected routes dùng `auth:sanctum` middleware

