## 🖥️ Console Commands Pattern

### Cấu trúc Command

**1. Đặt trong `app/Console/Commands/`**
```php
// app/Console/Commands/SyncAdsServiceUser.php
namespace App\Console\Commands;

use App\Models\ServiceUser;
use App\Repositories\ServiceUserRepository;
use App\Service\MetaBusinessService;
use Illuminate\Console\Command;

class SyncAdsServiceUser extends Command
{
    protected $signature = 'app:sync-ads-service-user';
    protected $description = 'Đẩy Job vào queue để đồng bộ các ads account';

    public function __construct(
        protected ServiceUserRepository $serviceUserRepository,
        protected MetaBusinessService $metaBusinessService,
    )
    {
        parent::__construct();
    }

    public function handle()
    {
        $this->serviceUserRepository->query()
            ->where('status', ServiceUserStatus::ACTIVE->value)
            ->chunkById(100, function ($serviceUsers) {
                $serviceUsers->each(function (ServiceUser $serviceUser) {
                    \App\Jobs\MetaApi\SyncMetaJob::dispatch($serviceUser);
                });
            });
    }
}
```

**2. Đăng ký Command trong `routes/console.php`**
```php
// routes/console.php
use Illuminate\Console\Scheduling\Schedule;

Schedule::command('app:sync-ads-service-user')->hourly();
```

**Lưu ý:**
- Signature format: `app:command-name` (kebab-case)
- Inject Repository/Service vào constructor
- Sử dụng `chunkById()` cho large datasets
- Đăng ký schedule trong `routes/console.php`

